). Helix &#x3B1;12b packs loosely with the H2TH helices (&#x3B1;10-&#x3B1;11) and helix &#x3B1;12 at the <span class="ins cts-4" title="Inserted by Sarumathi (eLife Sciences Publications, Ltd) - 01/8/2016 2:55pm" data-cid="88" data-userid="typesetter 6172" data-username="Sarumathi (eLife Sciences Publications, Ltd)" data-time="1452245117918">
'</span>
<span class="del cts-4" title="Deleted by Sarumathi (eLife Sciences Publications, Ltd) - 01/8/2016 2:55pm" data-cid="86" data-userid="typesetter 6172" data-username="Sarumathi (eLife Sciences Publications, Ltd)" data-time="1452245117858">
&#x201C;</span>
finger<span class="ins cts-4" title="Inserted by Sarumathi (eLife Sciences Publications, Ltd) - 01/8/2016 2:55pm" data-cid="90" data-userid="typesetter 6172" data-username="Sarumathi (eLife Sciences Publications, Ltd)" data-time="1452245122084">
