Figure 5</span>
.</p>
<img src="http://qa.elife.dev.cms30.kriyadocs.com/ecs/article/80792/resources/elife09584fs005[gl].jpg" data-primary-extension="tif" data-width="1772" data-height="1937" data-id="1737332" alt="http://qa.elife.dev.cms30.kriyadocs.com/ecs/article/80792/resources/elife09584fs005[gl].jpg" data-mce-src="http://qa.elife.dev.cms30.kriyadocs.com/ecs/article/80792/resources/elife09584fs005[gl].jpg" height="24" width="290"/></div>
<div class="jrnlFigBlock" id="BLK_F5-S2" data-stream-name="a_F5-S2">
<p class="jrnlFigCaption" id="F5-S2">
